Package: source-highlight
Version: 1.1
Revision: 11
Maintainer: Bill Bumgarner <bbum@codefab.com>
Source: gnu
SetCPPFLAGS: -no-cpp-precomp
UpdateConfigGuess: true
ConfigureParams: --mandir=%p/share/man
GCC: 3.1
InstallScript: make install DESTDIR=%d
DocFiles: README AUTHORS COPYING NEWS THANKS doc/*
Description: Programs to highlight source by syntax.
DescDetail: <<
GNU Source-highlight is a collection of programs that produces a document with syntax highlighting when given a source file. At the moment, it includes GNU java2html and GNU cpp2html.
<<
Homepage: http://www.gnu.org/software/src-highlite/
License: GPL
